copy.title: Harvest Hustle
copy.welcome_text: Heya, chickadee, welcome to Knothole Pantry! Let's organize snacks for all the little critters to eat! Match food in sets of 3 or more to send them to the storeroom!
copy.tutorial_try2: Grab the same kind of food when they're next to each other!
copy.tutorial_stepIntro: Welcome to Knothole Pantry! I'm gonna show you how to organize critter snacks for next season!
copy.tutorial_step2: Grab the same kinds of food when they're next to each other.
copy.tutorial_step3: There must be at least 3 pieces of food touching each other for you to grab them.
copy.tutorial_step4: If there are more than 3 pieces touching, you get more points!
copy.tutorial_step5: Here's where you can see how many snacks you need to collect for the little critters.
copy.tutorial_step6: I'll be here in case ya need me, 'kay?
copy.easy_story: Let's get the little stuff out of the way first, 'kay?
copy.medium_story: Boy, the Pantry is a MESS! Get ready to organize!
copy.hard_story: There's food EVERYWHERE! Get to it!
copy.royal_story: Hey, snack sortin' pro! Ready for a challenge? Start flappin'!
copy.all_story: Hi there Fairy Friend! Welcome to Sunflower Meadow! I'm sorting seeds to plant in the Spring. I get a little mixed up sometimes. Can you help me pick up pairs of seeds?
copy.easy_exitstory: Pretty good, chickadee! You're the best!
copy.hard_exitstory: Flaptastic job! Me an' all the little critters say thanks!
copy.royal_exitstory: Jumpin' jackrabbits, I've never seen Knothole Pantry so tidy! THANKS!
copy.allmedium_story: Keep goin'! There's so much more to do!
copy.allhard_story: Wow, you're good at this! Don't stop now!
copy.allroyal_story: Here comes the toughest part! Ready? Set? HUSTLE!
copy.instruction0: Match 3 or more pieces of the same kind of food to collect them.
copy.instruction1: The more food you match in one group, the more points you get!
copy.instruction2: If the food overflows the tree, the game is over.
copy.game_over_win_0: Wow, you're a top-notch harvest hustler, wings down! Thanks for helping the critters!
copy.game_over_win_1: I couldn't have done it without you. Thanks -- from me AND the critters!
copy.game_over_win_2: You're a harvest pro! Come back any time to hustle up more snacks, 'kay?
copy.game_over_win_3: There won't be a snack shortage now, that's for sure. Come back any time!
copy.game_over_win_4: This is great! We've got snacks galore! Come back again, 'kay? Thanks for your help!
copy.game_over_lose_0: Oops. Looks like things overloaded. But hey, you can try again any time! Thanks for helping!
copy.game_over_lose_1: Rats, things sort of... overflowed. But hey, why not try again? I can always use help!
copy.game_over_lose_2: Yikes! Harvest overload! Oh well, want to try again?
copy.level_tip_2: Collect 50 to get to the next level!
copy.level_tip_3: Don't let the rocks get in your way!
copy.level_tip_4: Use those buckets of Pixie Dust to make any match, 'cuz now you need to collect 60!
copy.level_tip_6: Keep flappin'! Collect 75 to get to the next level, 'kay?
copy.level_tip_7: Ooo, I LOVE neverberry cake! Hmm, I wonder what will happen if you touch one...?
copy.level_tip_9: Blueberries coming up! Now you have to collect 80.
copy.level_tip_10: I wonder what happens if you collect a blueberry cake? Oh, an' you need 90 to keep going!
copy.level_tip_13: Watch out, the swirly wind blows away a whole row! By the way, collect 100 this time!
copy.level_tip_19: Collect 110 pieces this time. Keep going!
copy.level_tip_26: You can collect 130, can't ya? 'Course you can!
copy.level_tip_30: Now there are walnuts to collect for the animals as well!
copy.level_tip_31: Water bubbles are a huge help. They clear everything around them!
copy.level_tip_40: Collect all 150 pieces of food here and you'll win the game! C'mon, do it, do it, get right to it!
copy.not_a_match_1: Make sure you have 3 of the same kind!
copy.tree_overflow_0: Look out! The tree is going to overflow!
copy.tree_overflow_1: Hurry! The food is almost to the top!
copy.match_0: Thunderin' thistles, that's a lot of food!
copy.match_big_0: That's a lot of food! Pat yourself on the wing!
copy.match_big_1: The little fuzzies will have a feast this winter!
copy.match_cake_red_1: Neverberries! Can't get enough of those!
copy.match_vortex_0: Swirly winds sure are helpful, huh?
copy.match_wildcard_0: Remember, buckets of Pixie Dust match anything!
copy.match_wildcard_1: Try to match as many as you can for the most points!
copy.match_bomb_0: Water bubbles clear everything around them!
copy.match_bomb_1: Aren't those water bubbles a big help!
copy.fall_rock_0: EEP, rock in the way! Oh no!
copy.fall_rock_1: Hurry, get rid of that rock!
copy.fall_vortex_1: There's another swirly wind! Go for it!
copy.host_level_1_0: Let's start small and work our way up, 'kay?
copy.host_level_1_2: Let's start out a little slow.
copy.host_level_2_1: If you stack 4 or more you get more points!
copy.host_level_4_0: Use the buckets of pixie dust to make a match!
copy.host_level_4_1: Look out for the rocks! They'll block your match!
copy.host_level_5_1: Okay, this one's a little tricky.
copy.host_level_6_0: 75 sounds like a lot, but you can do it!
copy.host_level_6_1: How long of a match can you do?
copy.host_level_8_0: The critters are grateful for your help!
copy.host_level_9_0: Oh, I LOVE blueberries, yum yum!
copy.host_level_10_0: Neverberry cakes are helpful. What about blueberry?
copy.host_level_10_1: See how many blueberries you can stack at once!
copy.host_level_11_0: They're coming faster! Keep it up!
copy.host_level_11_1: Get lots of cakes! They'll really speed things up!
copy.host_level_12_0: How many do you think you can get in one try?
copy.host_level_12_1: The critters will love all this chow! This is flaptastic!
copy.host_level_13_0: Click on the swirly wind to get rid of a row!
copy.host_level_13_1: Those rocks sure get in the way, don't they?
copy.host_level_14_0: The more you stack at once, the more points you get!
copy.host_level_14_1: I tell ya, the critters are gonna love you for this!
copy.host_level_15_0: You got the touch, chickadee! Keep it up!
copy.host_level_15_1: Try to get as many as you can at one time!
copy.host_level_16_0: The critters love neverberry cakes as much as I do!
copy.host_level_16_1: Yummy, corn! I can eat a whole kernel by myself, y'know.
copy.host_level_17_1: C'mon, fly as fast as your wings can flap!
copy.host_level_18_0: If you find 3 rocks together, match 'em to get 'em out of the way!
copy.host_level_18_1: Keep up the good work, chickadee!
copy.host_level_19_0: Boy, the critters do love those blueberry cakes!
copy.host_level_19_1: Click on the swirly wind if you need more time!
copy.host_level_20_1: Lots of critters love acorns! Do you like 'em?
copy.host_level_21_0: Keep stacking as fast as you can!
copy.host_level_22_0: Wow, you really know how to harvest!
copy.host_level_22_1: Remember, your hard work will really make a difference!

copy.host_level_24_0: Ooo, do you hear it? The critters' tummies are grumbling!
copy.host_level_25_0: Fly as fast as you can!
copy.host_level_26_0: See if you can get 5 kernels of corn at once!
copy.host_level_28_0: You have to fly fast here! Really flap those wings!
